Hi Sean,

We got further into the 2017 Skidoo MXZ X 850 for Dale Taylor, we had to remove the engine from chassis to be able to determine the issue. At this point we have a damaged MAG side piston, it appears to us that the connecting rod bearing has failed thus causing a grenade effect inside the engine.
